exhibition space.

TeX Pearls
++++++++++
We continue the tradition of the ?Pearls of TeX Programming?.
Metafont/MetaPost do also fall into that category. Details and
previously collected pearls can be found at
http://www.gust.org.pl/projects/pearls/.


